Employee Management Lightning Web 

Empoyee_ID:Number,Salary:Currency,Email:Email,Department:Picklist(IT,HR,Sales,Marketing,Finance),Joining_date:Date



Apex class:

public with sharing class EmployeeController {



    @AuraEnabled

    public static String saveEmployee(Employee_Record__c emp) {



        // Name Validation

        if(emp.Name == null ||

           emp.Name.length() < 3) {



            return 'Employee Name must contain at least 3 characters';

        }



        // Employee ID Validation

        if(emp.Employee_ID__c <= 0) {



            return 'Employee ID must be greater than 0';

        }



        // Unique Employee ID

        List<Employee_Record__c> existing =

        [SELECT Id FROM Employee_Record__c

         WHERE Employee_ID__c = :emp.Employee_ID__c

         LIMIT 1];



        if(existing.size() > 0) {



            return 'Employee ID already exists';

        }



        // Salary Validation

        if(emp.Salary__c < 10000 ||

           emp.Salary__c > 500000) {



            return 'Salary must be between 10,000 and 500,000';

        }



        // Email Validation

        String emailPattern =

        '^[A-Za-z0-9+_.-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+$';



        if(!Pattern.matches(emailPattern,

                            emp.Email__c)) {



            return 'Invalid Email Format';

        }



        // Department Validation

        if(String.isBlank(emp.Department__c)) {



            return 'Please select department';

        }



        // Joining Date Validation

        if(emp.Joining_Date__c > Date.today()) {



            return 'Joining Date cannot be future date';

        }



        insert emp;



        return 'SUCCESS';

    }

}

Validation Rule:

Name_Validation:LEN(Name) < 3:Employee Name must contain at least 3 characters

Employee_ID_Validation:Employee_ID__c <= 0:Employee ID must be greater than 0

Salary_Validation:OR(Salary__c < 10000,Salary__c > 500000):Salary must be between 10,000 and 500,000

Joining_Date_Validation:Joining_Date__c > TODAY():Joining Date cannot be future date



